h3 Additional Sizes
p.-text
  | Pagination supports a full spectrum of sizes: <code>-sm</code>, <code>-md</code>,
  |  <code>-lg</code>, <code>-xl</code>.
  | The default size is <code>-md</code>.
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--5
    each size in ['sm', 'md', 'lg', 'xl']
      nav(role='navigation', aria-label='Pagination').-pb--1
        ul.a-pagination(class=`-${size}`)
          each step in steps
            if step == '0'
              li
